{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Connexion{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="container mt-5">

    <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">Connexion</h1>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5">

            <form method="post">

                {% if error %}
                    <div class="alert alert-danger">
                        Identifiants invalides.
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if app.user %}
                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                        Vous êtes connecté en tant que {{ app.user.userIdentifier }}.
                        <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">Se déconnecter</a>
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="username" class="form-label">Adresse mail</label>
                    <input
                        type="email"
                        value="{{ last_username }}"
                        name="_username"
                        id="username"
                        class="form-control"
                        autocomplete="email"
                        required
                        autofocus
                    >
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label">Mot de passe</label>
                    <input
                        type="password"
                        name="_password"
                        id="password"
                        class="form-control"
                        autocomplete="current-password"
                        required
                    >
                </div>

                <input
                    type="hidden"
                    name="_csrf_token"
                    value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}"
                >

                <div class="d-grid">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">
                        Se connecter
                    </button>
                </div>

            </form>ChatGPT



Image chargée
je suis sous symfony laragon heidi sql ext je veux garder les boutons ou pas je sais pas mais comment puis je enjoliver cette page?

Oui, tu peux garder les boutons/nav actuels, mais ta page gagnerait beaucoup avec une carte de connexion moderne au centre.

Je te conseille :

Mettre le formulaire dans une card Bootstrap

Ajouter une petite icône au-dessus du titre

Donner un fond légèrement dégradé à la zone principale

Ajouter un lien “Mot de passe oublié ?”

Garder le bouton bleu, mais avec arrondi + ombre légère

Réduire un peu la hauteur vide entre le formulaire et le footer

Exemple simple avec Bootstrap :

<main class="login-page">
    <div class="login-card shadow-lg">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar login-icon"></i>
            <h1>Connexion</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">Accédez à votre espace MiniFacturier</p>
        </div>

        <form method="post">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="inputEmail" class="form-label">Adresse mail</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" id="inputEmail" class="form-control form-control-lg" required autofocus>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="inputPassword" class="form-label">Mot de passe</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="inputPassword" class="form-control form-control-lg" required>
            </div>

            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="remember_me" name="_remember_me">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="remember_me">
                        Se souvenir de moi
                    </label>
                </div>

                <a href="#" class="small">Mot de passe oublié ?</a>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg w-100 login-btn" type="submit">
                Se connecter
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</main>
Et le CSS :

.login-page {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #eaf2ff);
}

.login-card {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 520px;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
}

.login-card h1 {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #212529;
}

.login-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #0d6efd;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.login-btn {
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.8rem;
}

.form-control {
    border-radius: 0.7rem;
}
Moi je garderais la navbar et le footer, mais je transformerais surtout le formulaire en bloc central élégant, comme une vraie page d’application professionnelle.


mais je ne veux pass utriliser card

Parfait 👍 si tu ne veux pas utiliser de card Bootstrap, tu peux quand même obtenir un rendu moderne et propre sans ce composant. En fait, une card n’est rien d’autre qu’un conteneur stylé — on peut le recréer “à la main” avec du CSS plus fin.

👉 L’idée : garder une structure simple, mais jouer sur :

les espacements

les ombres légères

les bordures arrondies

un fond propre

💡 Version sans card (propre et moderne)
HTML (Twig)
<main class="login-page">
    <div class="login-container">

        <div class="login-header">
            <h1>Connexion</h1>
            <p>Accédez à votre espace MiniFacturier</p>
        </div>

        <form method="post">

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="inputEmail">Adresse mail</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" id="inputEmail" required autofocus>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="inputPassword">Mot de passe</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" id="inputPassword" required>
            </div>

            <div class="login-options">
                <label>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="_remember_me">
                    Se souvenir de moi
                </label>

                <a href="#">Mot de passe oublié ?</a>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="login-btn">
                Se connecter
            </button>

        </form>

    </div>
</main>
🎨 CSS (le vrai travail est ici)
.login-page {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #eaf2ff);
}

.login-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
}

/* Header */
.login-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.login-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.login-header p {
    color: #6c757d;
}

/* Champs */
.form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.form-group label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
}

.form-group input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.form-group input:focus {
    border-color: #0d6efd;
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(13,110,253,0.15);
}

/* Options */
.login-options {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

/* Bouton */
.login-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    background: #0d6efd;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: 0.3s;
}

.login-btn:hover {
    background: #0b5ed7;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}
🔥 Résultat
Sans utiliser card, tu obtiens :

un design moderne ✔️

centré ✔️

propre et pro ✔️

cohérent avec Symfony / Bootstrap ✔️

💬 Mon conseil (important)
👉 Tu peux garder ta navbar et ton footer (ils sont très bien)

👉 Le vrai problème de ta page actuelle :

trop “plate”

pas de hiérarchie visuelle

👉 Avec ce style :

le regard va direct sur le formulaire

ça fait appli SaaS (pro)

Si tu veux, je peux aller plus loin :
👉 version sombre
👉 animation au focus
👉 effet glassmorphism (très stylé 😏)


voici mon template actuel : login.html.twig :
{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Connexion{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="container mt-5">

    <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">Connexion</h1>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5">

            <form method="post">

                {% if error %}
                    <div class="alert alert-danger">
                        Identifiants invalides.
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if app.user %}
                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                        Vous êtes connecté en tant que {{ app.user.userIdentifier }}.
                        <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">Se déconnecter</a>
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="username" class="form-label">Adresse mail</label>
                    <input
                        type="email"
                        value="{{ last_username }}"
                        name="_username"
                        id="username"
                        class="form-control"
                        autocomplete="email"
                        required
                        autofocus
                    >
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label">Mot de passe</label>
                    <input
                        type="password"
                        name="_password"
                        id="password"
                        class="form-control"
                        autocomplete="current-password"
                        required
                    >
                </div>

                <input
                    type="hidden"
                    name="_csrf_token"
                    value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}"
                >

                <div class="d-grid">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">
                        Se connecter
                    </button>
                </div>

            </form>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>
{% endblock %}
mon base.html.twig :
<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>{% block title %}MiniFacturier{% endblock %}</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.13.1/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>

<body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100">

    {% include 'components/navbar.html.twig' %}

    <main class="container flex-grow-1 overflow-auto py-3 mt-5 pt-3">
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
    </main>

    {% include 'components/footer.html.twig' %}

    {# ===== MODAL MAILPIT ===== #}
    <div class="modal fade" id="mailpitModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">

                <div class="modal-header bg-dark text-white">
                    <h5 class="modal-title">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text me-2"></i>
                        Mailpit
                    </h5>

                    <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                </div>

                <div class="modal-body p-0">
                    <iframe
                        src="http://localhost:8026"
                        style="width: 100%; height: 80vh; border: none;"
                    ></iframe>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# ===== MODAL flash ===== #}
    {% for label, messages in app.flashes %}
        {% for message in messages %}
            <div class="modal fade" id="flashModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                    <div class="modal-content">

                        <div class="modal-header
                            {% if label == 'success' %}
                                bg-success text-white
                            {% elseif label == 'danger' %}
                                bg-danger text-white
                            {% else %}
                                bg-secondary text-white
                            {% endif %}
                        ">
                            <h5 class="modal-title">
                                {% if label == 'success' %}
                                    Succès
                                {% elseif label == 'danger' %}
                                    Erreur
                                {% else %}
                                    Information
                                {% endif %}
                            </h5>

                            <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="modal-body">
                            {{ message }}
                        </div>

                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                                Fermer
                            </button>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js/base.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js/stats.js') }}"></script>
    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}

</body>
</html>
mon home/index.html.twig :
<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>{% block title %}MiniFacturier{% endblock %}</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.13.1/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>

<body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100">

    {% include 'components/navbar.html.twig' %}

    <main class="container flex-grow-1 overflow-auto py-3 mt-5 pt-3">
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
    </main>

    {% include 'components/footer.html.twig' %}

    {# ===== MODAL MAILPIT ===== #}
    <div class="modal fade" id="mailpitModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">

                <div class="modal-header bg-dark text-white">
                    <h5 class="modal-title">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text me-2"></i>
                        Mailpit
                    </h5>

                    <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                </div>

                <div class="modal-body p-0">
                    <iframe
                        src="http://localhost:8026"
                        style="width: 100%; height: 80vh; border: none;"
                    ></iframe>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# ===== MODAL flash ===== #}
    {% for label, messages in app.flashes %}
        {% for message in messages %}
            <div class="modal fade" id="flashModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                    <div class="modal-content">

                        <div class="modal-header
                            {% if label == 'success' %}
                                bg-success text-white
                            {% elseif label == 'danger' %}
                                bg-danger text-white
                            {% else %}
                                bg-secondary text-white
                            {% endif %}
                        ">
                            <h5 class="modal-title">
                                {% if label == 'success' %}
                                    Succès
                                {% elseif label == 'danger' %}
                                    Erreur
                                {% else %}
                                    Information
                                {% endif %}
                            </h5>

                            <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="modal-body">
                            {{ message }}
                        </div>

                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                                Fermer
                            </button>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js/base.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js/stats.js') }}"></script>
    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}

</body>
</html>
mon navbar.html.twig :
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top">
    <div class="container">

        <a class="navbar-brand fw-semibold" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
            MiniFacturier
        </a>

        <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#mainNavbar"
        >
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="mainNavbar">

            <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">

                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-house me-1"></i> Accueil
                    </a>
                </li>

                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                    <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-group me-1"></i> Clients
                    </a>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_customer_index') }}">Liste des clients</a></li>

                        {% if is_granted('ROLE_ADMIN') or is_granted('ROLE_SELLER') %}
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_customer_new') }}">Ajouter un client</a></li>
                        {% endif %}
                    </ul>
                </li>

                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
